---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="About · 關於" description="About Dr Peggy and Body Wisdom Cards." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="about">
			<h1>
				<span class="i18n-zh">關於</span>
				<span class="i18n-en">About</span>
			</h1>
			<div class="prose">
				<div class="i18n-zh">
					<p>
						Dr Peggy 是一位身心整合工作者，致力於將神經科學、迷走神經理論與身體工作的洞見，
						翻譯成一份份溫柔、實用的邀請。
					</p>
					<p>
						《身體智慧卡》是一套陪伴 — 64 張卡片，從根基、綻放、深耕到傳遞，
						邀請你慢慢地，重新認識自己的身體。
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="i18n-en">
					<p>
						Dr Peggy is a somatic practitioner who translates insights from neuroscience,
						polyvagal theory, and body-based work into gentle, practical invitations.
					</p>
					<p>
						Body Wisdom Cards is a companion — 64 cards spanning Foundations, Blossoming,
						Deepening, and Offering, inviting you to listen to your body again, slowly.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
		<style>
			.about {
				max-width: 720px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 64px 24px 96px;
				color: var(--ink-soft);
			}
			.about h1 {
				font-family: var(--font-serif-zh);
				font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px);
				font-weight: 600;
				margin: 0 0 32px;
				color: var(--ink);
			}
			.about h1 .i18n-en { font-family: var(--font-sans); letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
			.prose p {
				font-size: 18px;
				line-height: 1.7;
				margin: 0 0 20px;
				color: var(--ink-soft);
			}
			.prose .i18n-zh p { font-family: var(--font-serif-zh); }
		</style>
	</body>
</html>
